OL,3,C'Not delivering': Special educational
OL,4,Cneeds system needs urgent reform
OL,6,FThe special educational needs system
OL,7,Fis "financially unsustainable" and in
OL,8,Furgent need of reform, the National
OL,9,FAudit Office (NAO) has said.
OL,11,FIn a report published on Thursday, NAO
OL,12,Fsaid families and children lack
OL,13,Fconfidence in the special educational
OL,14,Fneeds system due to "insufficient
OL,15,Fcapacity" within schools and longer
OL,16,Fwaiting times to support children.
