OL,6,FThursday's report comes after research
OL,7,Fshared exclusively with ITV News
OL,8,Frevealed that councils have already
OL,9,Famassed SEND deficits of #4 billion
OL,10,Fnationwide.
OL,12,FNAO'S report said: "(SEND is) still
OL,13,Fnot delivering better outcomes for
OL,14,Fchildren and young people or
OL,15,Fpreventing local authorities from
OL,16,Ffacing significant financial risks.
