OL,3,C'Not delivering': Special educational
OL,4,Cneeds system needs urgent reform
OL,6,F"DfE (Department for Education)
OL,7,Festimates that some 43% of local
OL,8,Fauthorities will have deficits
OL,9,Fexceeding or close to their reserves
OL,10,Fin March 2026.
OL,12,F"This contributes to a cumulative
OL,13,Fdeficit of between #4.3 billion and
OL,14,F#4.9 billion when accounting
OL,15,Farrangements that stop these deficits
OL,16,Fimpacting local authority reserves are
OL,17,Fdue to end. As such, the current
OL,18,Fsystem is not achieving value for
OL,19,Fmoney and is unsustainable."
