OL,3,C'Not delivering': Special educational
OL,4,Cneeds system needs urgent reform
OL,6,FNAO has urged the Government to
OL,7,Fconsider a "whole-system reform" to
OL,8,Fimprove outcomes for children with
OL,9,FSEND and put SEND provision on a
OL,10,F"financially sustainable footing".
OL,12,FIt added that the DfE should develop a
OL,13,F"long-term plan for inclusivity"
OL,14,Facross mainstream education.
