OL,3,C'Not delivering': Special educational
OL,4,Cneeds system needs urgent reform
OL,6,FGareth Davies, the head of the NAO,
OL,7,Fsaid: "Although DfE has increased high-
OL,8,Fneeds funding, the SEND system is
OL,9,Fstill not delivering for children and
OL,10,Ftheir families, and DfE's current
OL,11,Factions are unlikely to resolve the
OL,12,Fchallenges.
OL,14,F"The Government has not yet identified
OL,15,Fa solution to manage local authority
OL,16,Fdeficits arising from SEND costs,
OL,17,Fwhich ongoing savings programmes will
OL,18,Fnot address."
