OL,3,C'Not delivering': Special educational
OL,4,Cneeds system needs urgent reform
OL,6,FKate Foale, SEND spokeswoman for the
OL,7,FCCN, said: "With councils continuing
OL,8,Fto accrue spiralling deficits and
OL,9,Fdemand reaching record levels each
OL,10,Fyear, reform is urgent.
OL,12,F"The Government must set out root and
OL,13,Fbranch change to the system within the
OL,14,Fnext 18 months, designing a new way
OL,15,Fforward with strong input from local
OL,16,Fauthorities, parents and young people."
