OL,6,FCommenting on the NOA report, the
OL,7,FEducation Secretary Bridget Phillipson
OL,8,Fsaid: "The NAO's report exposes a
OL,9,Fsystem that has been neglected to the
OL,10,Fpoint of crisis, with children and
OL,11,Ffamilies with SEND quite simply being
OL,12,Ffailed on every measure.
OL,14,F"Every child and young person deserves
OL,15,Fthe best life chances and the
OL,16,Fopportunity to achieve and thrive.
