OL,6,F"But at the moment far too few are
OL,7,Fbeing given that chance in a system
OL,8,Fthat is too skewed towards specialist
OL,9,Fprovision and over-reliant on EHC
OL,10,Fplans ` often only to the benefit of
OL,11,Ffamilies who have the resources to
OL,12,Ffight for support.
OL,14,F"I am determined to rebuild families'
OL,15,Fconfidence in a system so many rely on
OL,16,F` so, there will be no more sticking
OL,17,Fplaster politics and short-termism
OL,18,Fwhen it comes to the life chances of
OL,19,Fsome of our most vulnerable children.
